// Trying to recreate the painting "Fishermen at sea" by William Turner
// https://www.tate.org.uk/art/artworks/turner-fishermen-at-sea-t01585

// I have rediscovered William Turner's paintings recently; 
// here is my take on this moonlight scene.
// Many elements are missing (including the fishermen themselves!),
// and the lighting is not quite on point, but I think it's already
// rather pretty.



// Inspired by "Seascape" by TDM
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/Ms2SD1

// My clouds are 2D, but their lighting was inspired by
// "Clouds" by iq
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/XslGRr

